    "actionPatterns": [
      "\\b(fix|implement|update|change|add|create|install|remove|delete)\\b",
      "(수정|구현|추가|생성|변경|설치|삭제|업데이트)(해|하고|해서|하자|하라|해라)",
      "(고치|만들)(고|거나|면)|고쳐|만들어"
    ],
    "noActionPatterns": [
      "(?:don't|do\\s+not)\\s+(?:change|edit|modify|fix|install|remove|delete)",
      "\\bno\\s+(?:edits?|changes?)\\b",
      "\\b(?:explain|describe)\\b[^.!?\\n]{0,160}\\bhow(?:\\s+(?:i|we|you|one|someone)\\s+(?:should|could|can|would))?\\s+(?:to\\s+)?(?:fix|implement|update|change|add|create|install|remove|delete)\\b",
      "(수정|구현|추가|생성|변경|설치|삭제|업데이트)하지\\s*마",
      "(고치|만들)지\\s*마",
      "(?:수정|구현|추가|생성|변경|설치|삭제|업데이트|고치|만들)(?:하는|할)?\\s*방법(?:만)?\\s*(?:을|를)?\\s*설명"
    ]
  },
